<p><a class="link" href="https://www.youtube.com/ZeeMusicCompany"  target="_blank" rel="noopener"
    >Zee Music Company</a><strong>MrBeast Hits 500M YouTube Subs: First Channel to Reach Milestone | Streams Charts</strong></p>
<p><a class="link" href="https://streamscharts.com/news/mrbeasts-youtube-channel-reaches-500-million-subscribers"  target="_blank" rel="noopener"
    >https://streamscharts.com/news/mrbeasts-youtube-channel-reaches-500-million-subscribers</a><strong>・関連記事</strong></p>
